{"id": 723, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年你又学会了什么无用技巧？", "description": "为聪慧的自己感到心酸。（题图来自：Josh Holinaty）", "record_count": 9820, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183535NezYDgOQVZFBpG5w.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-12-30T11:57:35Z", "options": [{"id": 38402, "content": "关你屁事？关我屁事？可以回答大部分问题。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276425}, {"id": 38403, "content": "一个人看电影 & 一个人做手术", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 62295}, {"id": 38404, "content": "学会了无数次面试未通过现在已经淡定了很多", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 377515}, {"id": 38917, "content": "一味追剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 317598}, {"id": 38406, "content": "学会了乐观对待世界上的不公平", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 397671}, {"id": 38407, "content": "看看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343242}, {"id": 40199, "content": "发呆，什么时候都能发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 415668}, {"id": 38408, "content": "学会了一个人生活却假装不孤单", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212020}, {"id": 38665, "content": "静静看着小婊砸们装逼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401976}, {"id": 38410, "content": "冬天，看猫在哪辆车的引擎盖栖息，就说明哪辆车刚到不久。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 395871}, {"id": 38411, "content": "假装自己不想谈恋爱！", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 399751}, {"id": 38412, "content": "学会了一个人宅着碰香水", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 309509}, {"id": 38413, "content": "学会了孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 399776}, {"id": 38414, "content": "不到十二点不考虑睡觉！！！！ ", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 186458}, {"id": 38926, "content": "知识/也许没用/依旧学习", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200812qkB48I0WiRp5ofsd.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 326848}, {"id": 38416, "content": "学会了一边吃火腿一边吃苹果  好吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161921}, {"id": 39441, "content": "一百元的焰火五颜六色", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 407954}, {"id": 42002, "content": "静静地看着她装B，却还能淡定的听着", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428170}, {"id": 38419, "content": "今年学会了怎么在悲伤的时候过滤自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263224}, {"id": 38420, "content": "理解了背着舅舅开家长会是一种什么样的体验", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 397792}, {"id": 38421, "content": "淡定地接受不公平的待遇，对不在期望范围内的事情快速进入状态面对", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248678}, {"id": 38422, "content": "学会瞬间插爽女朋友，瞬间发怒嗷嗷叫", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 399858}, {"id": 38423, "content": "学会了求无穷级数。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 344301}, {"id": 39704, "content": "别人忽悠我时 也不拆穿他 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410788}, {"id": 38425, "content": "一个人上班一个人下班一个人吃饭一个人看电影一个人睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360723}, {"id": 38426, "content": "斗图", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 399918}, {"id": 39450, "content": "工程制图", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 406992}, {"id": 38427, "content": "作为一个小白女生学会了装各种牛逼电脑软件并且找激活码以及根据攻略学会使用", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345789}, {"id": 38939, "content": "那个能找到各种奇♂怪网站的盆友能否把你的技能传授于我啊喂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276118}, {"id": 39196, "content": "再不起床出去耍就晚了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 406028}, {"id": 38429, "content": "知道赶不上飞机时，如何改签机票ToT", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260987}, {"id": 40221, "content": "找到了一个把磁力转化成种子下载的网站", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166423}, {"id": 38430, "content": "累死累活的为别人着想", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 399999}, {"id": 40734, "content": "我学会了逗逼的笑！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 397238}, {"id": 41246, "content": "上厕所省纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422808}, {"id": 38431, "content": "一个人看电影，一个人吃饭，一个人逛街，自嗨", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 399620}, {"id": 40735, "content": "钢琴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 383972}, {"id": 40991, "content": "红红火火", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 420858}, {"id": 41247, "content": "上厕所省纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422808}, {"id": 38432, "content": "得恋→失恋，很多人都觉得我成熟了", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200810ieVAk4mRBlT7w1IZ.jpg", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400033}, {"id": 38433, "content": "学会了不那么喜欢你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 108105}, {"id": 38945, "content": "解行李箱密码锁", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 402516}, {"id": 41249, "content": "上厕所省纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422808}, {"id": 38434, "content": "不那么冲动了，知道自己什么时候的话绝对不可以说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 51406}, {"id": 38435, "content": "学会了什么都不做如何躺一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400069}, {"id": 38436, "content": "学会了一个人去看电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 355122}, {"id": 38948, "content": "工作后，即使遇见看不惯的人，也依然会笑脸相迎。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 397231}, {"id": 38437, "content": "静静的看别人胡说八道然后一语道破", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400122}, {"id": 38438, "content": "认识到前一年的自己还是太幼稚了，这一年不论是身体还是心理成熟了好多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 337135}, {"id": 38187, "content": "无聊且累的时候打开韩剧然后放空自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 80679}]}